</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle f(x)={\frac {I_{r}-I_{\ell }}{2}}\left(\operatorname {erf} \left({\frac {x}{{\sqrt {2}}\sigma }}\right)+1\right)+I_{\ell }.}">
