<p>At the left side of the edge, the intensity is <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle I_{\ell }=\lim _{x\rightarrow -\infty }f(x)}">
