<p>while the gradient orientation can be estimated as
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle \theta =\operatorname {atan2} (L_{y},L_{x}).}">
