    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \partial _{vv}(L_{v})\leq 0.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/4b21d86531f5454c7a17fa701109946b33dd4db2" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:12.391ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="\partial _{vv}(L_{v})\leq 0."></span></dd></dl>
<p>Written out as an explicit expression in terms of local partial derivatives <span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle L_{x},L_{y},\ldots ,L_{yyy}}">
