<p>corresponding to the following filter masks:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle L_{xx}={\begin{bmatrix}1&amp;-2&amp;1\end{bmatrix}}L\quad {\text{and}}\quad L_{xy}={\begin{bmatrix}-1/4&amp;0&amp;1/4\\0&amp;0&amp;0\\1/4&amp;0&amp;-1/4\end{bmatrix}}L\quad {\text{and}}\quad L_{yy}={\begin{bmatrix}1\\-2\\1\end{bmatrix}}L.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
